Karen Austin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Karen_Austin 0 Karen Austin (born October 24, 1955) is an American actress. She played Lana Wagner on the sitcom Night Court in 1984. Her film appearances include Summer Rental (1985), Jagged Edge (1985), and The Ladies Club (1986). Karen_Austin ( born October_24_,_1955 ) is an_American_actress .
